; Standard COM in-proc server exports required for a credential provider DLL.
; LogonUI loads the provider via CoCreateInstance -> DllGetClassObject.
; DllRegisterServer / DllUnregisterServer support explicit, scripted
; registration (see README.md, "Registry registration model" - no interactive
; regsvr32 workflow in production, but the exports keep local testing simple).
LIBRARY

EXPORTS
    DllGetClassObject   PRIVATE
    DllCanUnloadNow     PRIVATE
    DllRegisterServer   PRIVATE
    DllUnregisterServer PRIVATE
